<div style="text-align: center;"><b>COMPANY PROFILE</b></div><div><br></div><div style="text-align: justify;">Davao Sweet Temptation Incorporated, a family owned company headed by its President,&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 1rem;">Mr. John Goldeto T. Baricuatro was established in 1997 with an objective of bringing the&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 1rem;">“Goldilocks” brand in Davao.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 1rem;">It started its operations in Victoria Plaza having a 4 sqm. store in front of the grocery section&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 1rem;">as a retailer of the brand.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 1rem;">A year after, it expanded to the newly built Gaisano Mall of Davao and integrated its dine in&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 1rem;">setting just to test the market.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 1rem;">In 2002, a plant was put in placed by Goldilocks Bakeshop itself to support the increasing&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 1rem;">demand for the brand in Davao and the entire Mindanao and making Davao Sweet&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 1rem;">Temptation as the first ever Franchisee in Mindanao.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 1rem;">Today, Davao Sweet Temptation Incorporated remains as the number one Franchisee of&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 1rem;">Goldilocks Bakeshop.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 1rem;">It has expanded hand in hand with the franchisor and has expanded with several stores&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 1rem;">mostly located inside the malls.</span></div><div style="text-align: justify;">Davao Sweet Temptation Incorporated will continue to grow and will fill in the gap for the&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 1rem;">needs of the brand in Mindanao.</span></div><div><br></div><div style="text-align: center;"><b>VISION</b></div><div><br></div><div style="text-align: justify;">DSTI envisions to be the leading and dynamic provider of value added products in the food&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 1rem;">industry, renowned for the best quality produce, win-win partnerships that constantly&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 1rem;">delight consumers, and aspiring to become the most admired company in our industry as&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 1rem;">seen by our stakeholders.</span></div><div><br></div><div style="text-align: center;"><b>MISSION</b></div><div><br></div><div style="text-align: justify;">We are steadfast in our commitment to fulfill gainful yet ethical means to provide top&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 1rem;">quality products, where the company aims to have a socially and environmentally&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 1rem;">responsible corporate philosophy geared towards the improvement of our stakeholders and</span></div><div style="text-align: justify;">the Filipino consumers.</div><div><br></div><div>Click the <a href="http://test.johngold.dev.dcideasandsolutions.com/pages/37" title="" target="">link</a> to view branches</div>